#

Polish Borscht with Sausage

45 min
$15
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

Polish

Course:

Main

Tags:

HeartyComfort FoodSoup

Description

A hearty beet soup with flavorful sausage, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 4 medium, peeled and grated
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • potatoes: 2 medium, diced
  • carrots: 1 large, diced
  • onion: 1 large, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • smoked sausage: 1 pound, sliced
  • fresh dill: 1 bunch, chopped
  • sour cream: 1 cup, for serving
